180.question: What is the accuracy of the proposed technique?
180.response: {'Answer': 'TUPLEINF has an accuracy of 51.7% for 4th grade and 51.6% for 8th grade when used alone according to Table 2. When combined with IR, as in Table 3, the accuracy improves to 55.3% for 4th grade and 55.1% for 8th grade.'}
180.answer: 51.7 and 51.6 on 4th and 8th grade question sets with no curated knowledge. 47.5 and 48.0 on 4th and 8th grade question sets when both solvers are given the same knowledge
